item.title: I need help
item.dc:creator: @DcnScape DcnScape
item.description:
@DcnScape wrote:

Are you wanting to use Smf? If not then www.webs.com is another great free website building site. Now about the domain, you are going to have to use the domain they give you. Unless you go want to go with a .tk domain which can be found at www.dot.tk. If you want to go a little more advanced depending what your using, I know if you use www.webs.com I believe it’s around $21.99 a year for a .com domain. Other free website creating site’s may be different, they may have there own domain you can purchase or you purchase one from a site. I will give you a few example’s below:

  1. www.order.1and1.com
  2. www.godaddy.com
  3. www.Register.com

I’m sure there is several more, but those are some I found that are fair prices.
